info.author: Tamas Haraszti
info.description:
This is a developmental package to access the functionality of the dc1394 in
python. Since I preferred a simplistic approach, it is based on plain C and the
python basic API. See also the webpage.
info.name: Dc1394
info.summary: Python wrapper functions to the dc1394 firewire camera library
